dotaz_ockovani: select datum, sum(pocet) from ockovani_lide ol where datum>'2021-07-01' and kraj_nazev ='Hlavní město Praha' and vakcina  like 'Comirnaty' and zarizeni_kod ='00023001000' group by datum;
